name: Did a Business
tagline: You call it wasted time, I call it transferable skills
body:
### Welcome to Did a Business
The objective: retire at 35 with $15,000,000 in the bank, and live off interest and dividends while impacting positive change in the world wherever and whenever possible. 

Is this a pipe dream? Can it be done? What are the steps one must take?

Join me as I try to figure it out, with the help from my trusted friends and industry experts. 

### Let's make moves!
